<HEADLINE> Thrashers Get Lambert </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ATLANTA (AP) -- The Atlanta Thrashers acquired left wing Denny  
Lambert from the Nashville Predators on Monday in exchange for the 
rights to center Randy Robitaille. 
</P>
