<HEADLINE>  Armstrong Competes on Mountain Bike </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	MONTPELIER, Vt. (AP) -- For his first bicycle race in the United  
States since winning the Tour de France, Lance Armstrong is giving 
up his skinny road racing tires for the fat nobbies of a mountain 
bike. 
</P>
<P>
